name: MOFE
description:
This work is part of SMS (Senam Minggu Sehat) joint project, a weekly gymnastics agenda held in Wonosari town square, held for free for everyone to participate. But usually, the participant are dominated by young women and mothers.

We try to compose a music which is acceptable to all ages, and can certainly be used as background music for gymnastics. The work in this audio utilizes elements from Javanese pelog tone as the main framework, wrapped with the distinctive mood of common SKJ music to be easily accepted.
